title: Alabama-Clemson, Trevor Lawrence, the Packers, and NFL rumors
itunes:title: Alabama-Clemson, Trevor Lawrence, the Packers, and NFL rumors
description:
Colin discusses what was surprising about the Alabama-Clemson Championship game, what the scouts are already saying about Clemson Tigers QB Trevor Lawrence, why he doubts Green Bay Packers new HC Matt LaFleur, and the latest NFL coaching rumors. Guests include Joel Klatt, Peter Schrager, Rashad Jennings, and Tony Gonzalez.
